{{Otheruses|Trade Council}}
The '''Prackla Trade Council''' was an association of businessbeings and merchants established during the last decades of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Cartao/Legends|Cartao]], with the aim of furthering business interests on Cartao and the [[Prackla sector/Legends|Prackla sector]] as a whole.

Although the Prackla Trade Council had a clearly-defined mission, the general consensus among independent traders and businessbeings was that the Council members worked for their own, personal gain, and not that of the membership.

